snippet.title: Game Soup Trailer - On Steam Feb. 11!
snippet.description:
Our second game, Game Soup, releases February 11th! Check it out here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/981420/Game_Soup/

We also made Infernal Racket:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/664510/Infernal_Racket/

You can help support Game Soup:
Patreon - http://www.patreon.com/gamesoup
Paypal - GameSoupLP@gmail.com
Bitcoin - 3QFv3iqkc1Mb192dNQzjsFEcbe3SRT7BwD

Twitter: https://twitter.com/gamesouplp
Discord: https://discord.gg/n23C7Fp

We have an analysis-only channel (no Let's Plays): https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCPbq5s9zheSKNAnEmBbo1_w

Thanks for watching! ツ
GameSoupLP at gmail.com
